Celebrity casanova and controversial businessman Nico Matlala is once again the subject of allegations of a scam by one of his ex-girlfriends claiming he made off with her hard-earned cash. The latest alleged victim, Sello Ledwaba, is a banker from Matlala's hometown of Polokwane, Limpopo, but based in Pretoria. Ledwaba claims that Matlala did not only leave her with a bleeding heart but left her purse with a R140000 hole after he borrowed money from her to use towards his construction business. TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE